≈ыWarchive/external_nushell_repo_backup/nushell.github.io/blog/2019-10-15-nushell-0_4_0.mdы@7313b05581591408228d7d1238efb12bff8d1449156ddbc21fac5cd96238df5eЄtitle: Nushell 0.4.0▒╬Onto the Beta compiler (est31)з╝For those of you wondering if and when Nu was going to be usable on stable Rust, you need but wait just a little longer. Contributor est31 has been hard at work at moving Nu onto stable Rust and has now successfully moved Nu off of nightly and onto beta. As beta matures and becomes the next release of Rust, we'll be able to move Nu onto stable. This should help people who are working to distribute Nu on various distributions.
▓░░зЬTitle: title: Nushell 0.4.0
Path: Onto the Beta compiler (est31)
Content:
For those of you wondering if and when Nu was going to be usable on stable Rust, you need but wait just a little longer. Contributor est31 has been hard at work at moving Nu onto stable Rust and has now successfully moved Nu off of nightly and onto beta. As beta matures and becomes the next release of Rust, we'll be able to move Nu onto stable. This should help people who are working to distribute Nu on various distributions.
